{{!--
/**
 * Settings Dialog Footer Template
 *
 * PURPOSE:
 * Reusable footer component for settings dialogs providing standard Cancel
 * and Save button controls. Ensures consistent button presentation and
 * functionality across all settings dialogs with proper accessibility
 * attributes and icon usage.
 *
 * CONTEXT REQUIREMENTS:
 * This template is largely static and does not require dynamic context data.
 *
 * HELPER DEPENDENCIES:
 * @requires localize - Foundry VTT localization helper for button text translation
 *
 * ACCESSIBILITY FEATURES:
 * - Semantic form footer structure
 * - Button elements with descriptive text and icons
 * - Icons marked as decorative with aria-hidden="true"
 * - Clear action differentiation through button types and classes
 *
 * CUSTOMIZATION POINTS:
 * - Consistent button styling across all settings dialogs
 * - Standard Cancel/Save action pattern
 * - Icon usage for visual action identification
 * - Reusable component for dialog standardization
 *
 * INTEGRATION:
 * - Used across multiple settings dialogs for consistency
 * - Provides standard dialog action controls
 * - Uses module localization keys from SPELLBOOK.UI namespace
 * - Supports form submission and cancellation workflows
 */
--}}

<div class="form-footer">
  <!-- Cancel Button -->
  <button type="button" class="cancel-button" data-action="close">
    <i class="fas fa-times" aria-hidden="true"></i>
    {{localize "SPELLBOOK.UI.Cancel"}}
  </button>

  <!-- Save Button -->
  <button type="submit" class="save-button">
    <i class="fas fa-save" aria-hidden="true"></i>
    {{localize "SPELLBOOK.UI.Save"}}
  </button>
</div>
